Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.11,0:00:18.62,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Splendidly done, brave heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.20,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.79,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy yourselves to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.71,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.92,main,Nob1,0000,0000,0000,,That's the heroes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.96,main,Nob2,0000,0000,0000,,Our country has nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.72,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:35.97,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have come here \Nif it wasn't for the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.93,main,Nob3,0000,0000,0000,,I hear the casualties were in \Nthe single digits this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:43.10,main,Nob4,0000,0000,0000,,Bless our heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:46.65,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,I held my ground against a massive monster
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.32,main,Cap,0000,0000,0000,,and fought with pride as a royal knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.86,top,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:53.53,main,Nob5,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly honored to meet you, Spear Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.82,main,Nob6,0000,0000,0000,,Do you happen to have a lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.12,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama is still \Ntired from the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.33,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.12,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.80,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:17.72,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.26,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,The food here seems heavenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to eat, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:24.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You should join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:25.60,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.53,sign_16244_165_When_two_more_wi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1399,223)}Persons or objects can be registered to allow them to be\Nteleported with you when summoned by the hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:36.70,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport people with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:42.83,sign_16244_165_When_two_more_wi,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1399,223)}Persons or objects can be registered to allow them to be\Nteleported with you when summoned by the hourglass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.74,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd noticed this sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:53.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.51,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.31,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Duel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:32.25,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:48.58,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(438,596)}Lullaby at Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:50.54,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Raphtalia-chan's your slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And what if she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.58,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia is my slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:02.26,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! It's not right to enslave others!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:07.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Slavery is legal in this country, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.85,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,But we're heroes from another world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.98,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,We can't behave that way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.02,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.44,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, free Raphtalia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And what if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:29.70,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Then... you can keep things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.25,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.29,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,He has a slave in his party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.71,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he couldn't stoop \Nany lower, but he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.67,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard your conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:48.18,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,A hero, using a demi-human as his slave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.14,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you are rotten to the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:57.06,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I order you to accept his challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.65,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.40,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with Naofumi-sama \Nof my own free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.85,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:07.82,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:11.33,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You've been placed under a curse that \Ncompels you to defend your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.71,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:18.33,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Once Motoyasu-dono wins, we shall \Nrelease you from that curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.13,main,Kni,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.64,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't heed my order,\NI shall take her from you by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.47,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not thinking \Nof running from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, you'd better return Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.52,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,And how exactly will you win, {\i1}Shield{\i0} Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:55.37,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,The duel between the \NSpear Hero and the Shield Hero will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:06:02.25,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,This duel will end when one of the \Ncombatants is pinned or admits defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.05,sign_33122_363_Legendary_Weapon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Legendary Weapon Rule Violation:\NHolding non-assigned weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:22.90,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,This duel will take place in the presence \Nof King Melromarc and the Pope,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.28,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,and it is thus legitimate and official.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.91,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.45,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Best of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:41.79,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that folk tale about the\Nirresistible spear and the immovable shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:47.30,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi, be a man and admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.14,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.14,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.65,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.57,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're not the \NShield Hero for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.24,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.37,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,In this battle between an irresistible \Nspear and an immovable shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,you lost the moment you \Ncouldn't pierce my shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.13,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:40.98,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.48,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,A strike using the shield? It would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.36,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.53,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.70,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,A balloon? What's that doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.29,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:05.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't win anyway, I might as \Nwell make you as miserable as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.42,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.67,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.80,sign_25674_228_The_Village_of_L,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(447,1)}Two-Headed Black Dog Shield \NExclusive Skill: Dog Bite
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.64,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.61,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.65,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.24,top,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! Knock it off, \Nyou cowardly cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.15,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.24,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,If this keeps up, the Shield Hero might win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.58,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-san's got the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.20,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:47.13,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,What does that lowly Shield Hero \Nthink he's doing to the Spear Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:50.00,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Have you no respect for \Nthe sanctity of a duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be embarrassed \Neven more, Mr. Hot Stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.93,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who would ever surrender now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:12.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I focus the attacks on \Nyour face and your crotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cowardly cheat, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:17.45,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.46,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.38,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.50,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Someone interfered in our one-on-one duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.19,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Your party member messed up that duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.78,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Sore loser much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone there saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:42.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Myne use her magic, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know you saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She used her magic to help him win...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No... There's no way they didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:56.26,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to listen\N to the words of scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.46,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Spear Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.68,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,you are the victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.26,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.26,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Motoyasu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.10,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:17.53,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Hero, I know you must feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:22.24,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,It's really too bad that you'll \Nhave to go back to fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.04,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You were brilliant, Motoyasu-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.67,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter, Malty, was right to pick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.09,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:43.26,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I was so shocked when I \Nheard Myne was a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.22,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.22,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,But I fight to contribute\Nto the world's peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:52.73,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,So these guys planned everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.69,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,The daughter framed me to get in the \Ngood graces of her favorite hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:03.74,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,And the father distorted the facts \Nfor the sake of his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:07.70,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This duel was a setup all along, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:11.21,flashback,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero has forced \Nthat girl to be his slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.83,flashback,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Please save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:21.97,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do they want to see me suffer that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.05,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come to this world \Nbecause I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.89,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who summoned me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.81,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.35,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why must I alone go through this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:40.78,main,Min,0000,0000,0000,,The girl enslaved by the Shield Hero \Nhas been freed by the Spear Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:45.95,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,We should never have summoned \Nthe Shield Hero, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.87,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,The other three are more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.41,main,W,0000,0000,0000,,We should just get rid of \Nthat criminal scum at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:53.29,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Our country doesn't need the Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.08,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Execute the Shield Hero right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about the Shield again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.01,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm the Shield Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.64,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.73,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's free the girl from her curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.16,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:36.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.09,sign_22916_178_Slave_pact_with_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Slave pact with Raphtalia terminated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.34,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,You're free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.34,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful for the charity \NMotoyasu-sama showed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's it... I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.26,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A world like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,...can die for all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.73,sign_24196_186_Curse_Series_Req,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Curse Series Requirement Met
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.02,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.73,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing to Motoyasu-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:49.45,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ask you to free me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:53.62,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,B-But he was abusing you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you know \Nabout Naofumi-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:15:01.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,He never made me do anything I couldn't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:06.55,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,He only activated the curse when \NI was too scared to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.38,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.26,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody should be forced to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama can't use any weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:16.72,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else has to fight for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:18.39,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:20.60,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,He'll just abuse you until you break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.23,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama defends me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.36,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,He lets me rest when I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.36,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not that kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:35.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you capable of extending a hand to \Na diseased slave on the verge of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:41.00,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama fed me everything \NI wanted to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:45.75,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me valuable medicine \Nto treat my illness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:47.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are {\i1}you{\i0} capable of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.38,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:54.93,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,If that were true, you would \Nhave a slave by your side, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:57.47,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.43,top,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.31,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, damned demi-human?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.31,main,Nob,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.48,main,Nob,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.65,main,Nob,0000,0000,0000,,A quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:11.36,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Myne-san, I'd like to ask you about \Nyour illegal interference in the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.28,main,Malt,0000,0000,0000,,What ever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.57,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:18.33,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,You lost that duel, Motoyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:22.54,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone{\i0} shot a magic spell at Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.71,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to tell, though, \Nbecause it was wind magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.75,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Myne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.00,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,You must've imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.55,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,The audience didn't see a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.63,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,The king has told them to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.30,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,One look at the nobles' \Neyes makes it obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:39.52,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe royalty \Nwould debase a sacred duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.86,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,To laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:16:59.83,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.42,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I heard rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:11.38,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,They called you the horrible hero who \Nforced himself on a party member.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:16.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But I think you wouldn't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:17.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the oh-so-charitable Motoyasu,\N you're free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay clear of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:41.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Or what, did he tell you to go get \Na good look at the loser's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Please just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:56.18,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.89,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do to make you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Believe you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,After you betrayed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.65,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be on your side,\Ncome what may!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that to trick me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:13.61,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:14.44,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What else are you people \Ngoing to frame me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.99,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I drew the short straw \Nthe moment I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.29,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Try as I might, nobody will accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.87,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody believes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this damn thing, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:39.01,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This shield has saved my \Nlife many times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.68,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,And during the Wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.60,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you couldn't fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:48.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,you defended the villagers using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:53.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really do it for the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:57.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you saved many, many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that nice a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.49,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you as nothing but \Na tool at first, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I was only thinking of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:25.81,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I know you better than \Nanyone else in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.10,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I know how kind you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:34.52,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,So even if the whole world speaks ill of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.53,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.78,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell them again and again \Nthat you're a wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.74,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who saved \Nmy life, gave me a sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,and showed me my purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:58.05,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow you through fire and brimstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.93,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Those were the words I always \Nwished someone would say to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.51,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just didn't hear her before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.18,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I am your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.69,flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you go, I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:24.37,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't trust \Nanyone anymore, I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.95,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you, the man who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, I trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.50,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,...the great Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.30,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.81,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:51.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But... Raphtalia's still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.56,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.48,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,When will you stop treating me like a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:00.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, sure, I'm still an unreliable \Nkid who cries at the drop of a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.82,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I may even be a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:07.45,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But please let me stand by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.79,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I need you, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:33.68,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:37.05,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong is a hero having a slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:41.11,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan might still be doing \Nall this because she's brainwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:42.69,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:48.11,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you can say that \Nafter seeing them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:55.32,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But from now, let me share in your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.91,0:22:19.61,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Naofumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:33.14,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's only leftovers from the castle \Nkitchen and some bread, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.79,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} Raphtalia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.45,0:22:45.61,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,When demi-humans level up as children,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:48.27,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,their bodies follow suit \Nand grow rapidly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:55.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's why demi-humans are seen as inhuman \Nbeasts and discriminated against.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:56.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:00.49,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,For leftovers, it's quite good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:10.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.78,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can taste it. It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:20.63,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat lots of delicious \Nfood from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.03,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:26.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.36,0:23:28.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:39.97,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}Filo
